## API Specification

### Authentication

| Method | Endpoint | Body | Response | Auth |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| `POST` | `/api/auth/register` | `{ name, email, password }` | `{ user, token }` | No |
| `POST` | `/api/auth/login` | `{ email, password }` | `{ user, token }` | No |
| `GET` | `/api/auth/me` | — | `{ user }` | Yes |

### Habits

| Method | Endpoint | Body | Response | Auth |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/api/habits` | — | `{ habits: Habit[] }` | Yes |
| `POST` | `/api/habits` | `{ name, emoji, frequency }` | `{ habit: Habit }` | Yes |
| `PUT` | `/api/habits/:id` | `{ name, emoji, frequency }` | `{ habit: Habit }` | Yes |
| `DELETE` | `/api/habits/:id` | — | `{ success: true }` | Yes |
| `PATCH` | `/api/habits/:id/toggle` | `{ date: "YYYY-MM-DD" }` | `{ habit: Habit }` | Yes |

### Routines

| Method | Endpoint | Body | Response | Auth |
|---|---|---|---|---|
| `GET` | `/api/routines` | — | `{ routines: RoutineItem[] }` | Yes |
| `POST` | `/api/routines` | `{ period, name, timeEstimate }` | `{ routine: RoutineItem }` | Yes |
| `PUT` | `/api/routines/:id` | `{ name, timeEstimate }` | `{ routine: RoutineItem }` | Yes |
| `DELETE` | `/api/routines/:id` | — | `{ success: true }` | Yes |
| `PATCH` | `/api/routines/:id/toggle` | `{ date: "YYYY-MM-DD" }` | `{ routine: RoutineItem }` | Yes |
| `PATCH` | `/api/routines/reorder` | `{ period, itemIds: string[] }` | `{ routines: RoutineItem[] }` | Yes |

### Error Response Format (Consistent)

```typescript
{
  error: string,       // Machine-readable code: "VALIDATION_ERROR", "NOT_FOUND", etc.
  message: string,     // Human-readable message
  details?: ZodError[] // Validation field errors (only for validation failures)
}
```

### HTTP Status Codes

| Code | Meaning |
|---|---|
| `200` | Success |
| `201` | Created |
| `400` | Validation error / Bad request |
| `401` | Not authenticated |
| `403` | Not authorized (trying to access another user's data) |
| `404` | Resource not found |
| `409` | Conflict (duplicate email on register) |
| `500` | Internal server error |

