## Proposed Changes (Ordered by Dependency)

### Phase 1: Infrastructure

#### [NEW] `.env.local`
- `MONGODB_URI` — Connection string to MongoDB Atlas
- `NEXTAUTH_SECRET` — Random 32-char secret for JWT signing
- `NEXTAUTH_URL` — Base URL (http://localhost:3000 for dev)

#### [NEW] `.env.example`
- Template file with placeholder values for all env vars

#### [NEW] [db.ts](file:///d:/projects%20in%202026/visionboard/src/lib/db.ts)
- Mongoose connection singleton with connection caching (critical for serverless where each request may re-initialize)
- Handles reconnection and error logging

