### Phase 7: Frontend Integration

#### [NEW] [api-client.ts](file:///d:/projects%20in%202026/visionboard/src/lib/api-client.ts)
- Typed fetch wrapper with automatic token injection from NextAuth session
- Error handling with typed error responses
- Methods: `get<T>()`, `post<T>()`, `put<T>()`, `patch<T>()`, `delete<T>()`

#### [MODIFY] [habit-store.ts](file:///d:/projects%20in%202026/visionboard/src/store/habit-store.ts)
- Replace localStorage persistence with API calls
- Implement **optimistic updates**: update Zustand state immediately, then sync with server
- On error: rollback to previous state and show toast message
- Add `loadHabits()` action to fetch from API on mount
- Remove `persist` middleware (server is now the source of truth)

#### [MODIFY] [routine-store.ts](file:///d:/projects%20in%202026/visionboard/src/store/routine-store.ts)
- Same pattern as habit-store: optimistic updates + API calls
- Transform API response (flat list) into the `Record<RoutinePeriod, RoutineItem[]>` structure the UI expects

#### [MODIFY] [index.ts](file:///d:/projects%20in%202026/visionboard/src/types/index.ts)
- Add `User` type, `ApiResponse<T>` wrapper type, `ApiError` type
- Update [Habit](file:///d:/projects%20in%202026/visionboard/src/types/index.ts#1-9) and [RoutineItem](file:///d:/projects%20in%202026/visionboard/src/types/index.ts#10-16) to use `_id` from MongoDB (with client alias to [id](file:///d:/projects%20in%202026/visionboard/src/components/habits/habit-grid.tsx#7-80))

#### [MODIFY] [layout.tsx](file:///d:/projects%20in%202026/visionboard/src/app/layout.tsx)
- Wrap app in NextAuth `SessionProvider`

#### [MODIFY] [page.tsx](file:///d:/projects%20in%202026/visionboard/src/app/page.tsx)
- Add auth check: redirect to `/login` if not authenticated
- Call `loadHabits()` and `loadRoutines()` on mount

#### [MODIFY] [header.tsx](file:///d:/projects%20in%202026/visionboard/src/components/dashboard/header.tsx)
- Add user menu (avatar + name + logout button) using `UserMenu` component

